name: GLOW green GAS MASK TEE
description: For the guys! This shirt features a hand stenciled gas mask graphic in the front. The graphic was overlaid with GLOW in the dark paint. It is surrounded by sporadic neon green stitching. Neon stitching outlines the entire shirt, ending with stitched sound waves going down the back of the shirt. Fucking sexy. SZ. L

name: NOT REALLY PiNK TOP
description: Re constructed top. There’s a hand stenciled Manga inspired girl on the front accented with neon orange stitching. All seams are enforced with neon orange, and theres a “splat” shape and the word “PUKE” stitched into the back. BLAGGGHHH!!!

name: The COMBAT SKiRT
description:
Tank girl? Yessssss.
Long skirts are sick! This ones made of a light weight black denim with a little stretch in it. There are 5 recycled snake skin fabric star appliqués scattered about (2 on the front, 3 on the back), 4 D-rings on the right side, middle back silt, decorative zippers on the back, and 2 pockets on the front of this skirt. The drawstring waist plus the stretchy fabric makes it very versatile in sizing. If its too long for you I can adjust it prior to shipping free of charge.

	Measurements:
Length: 39.5” 
Waist: 34” (drawstring waist)
Slit: 20.5

name: FUNKY SOFT SECTiONED SCARF
description: This super cool scarf keeps you warm in the winter and fabulous all year round! Its made of super soft fleece, black and white striped heavy satin, and lime green fur [fake, of course]. It is sectioned off into 3 parts, each having their own appliqués. I’ll have the measurements up in a bit, but its basically big enough to drape around the neck a few times.

name: MEDUSA Legwarmers
description:
These completely original pair of warmers are art for your legs! They are made out of 5 different types of fabric, rocket blue, neon green, and black thread, non slip elastic, and love. The elastic makes them very versicle in sizing, but I’d say they would fit sizes S-L. Oh, and they really do keep your legs warm.
